WEBVTT

12:55.040 --> 12:56.820 line:80%
she's a jinx!

12:57.280 --> 12:58.950 line:80%
Only you and your husband,

12:58.950 --> 13:00.590 line:80%
who have no one to bury you when you die,

13:00.590 --> 13:02.780 line:80%
took in this whole cursed family.

13:02.880 --> 13:04.120 line:80%
Maybe one day,

13:04.120 --> 13:06.050 line:80%
she'll bring you to your death too.
